OL,3,COasis among Brits set for Rock and
OL,4,CRoll Hall of Fame induction
OL,6,FOasis are among the Brits to be
OL,7,Finducted into the Rock and Roll Hall
OL,8,Fof Fame in Los Angeles this year.
OL,10,FA total of six British entries will be
OL,11,Fhonoured this year, including Phil
OL,12,FCollins, Sade, rocker Billy Idol and
OL,13,FManchester icons Joy Division and New
OL,14,FOrder, who share a single nomination.
OL,16,FThe 2026 honourees were announced by
OL,17,FRyan Seacrest during an episode of
OL,18,FAmerican Idol.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
