OL,3,COasis among Brits set for Rock and
OL,4,CRoll Hall of Fame induction
OL,6,FCollins' 2026 induction will be his
OL,7,Fsecond, having previously been
OL,8,Fhonoured as a member of Genesis in
OL,9,F2010.
OL,11,FJoy Division and New Order share a
OL,12,Fsingle induction, with the latter
OL,13,Fformed by the remaining members after
OL,14,Fthe 1980 death of Joy Division lead
OL,15,Fsinger Ian Curtis.
OL,17,FRock and Roll Hall of Fame chairman
OL,18,FJohn Sykes said: "Induction into the
OL,19,FRock & Roll Hall of Fame is music's
OL,20,Fhighest honour.
OL,26,@zD@ROU
