OL,3,COasis among Brits set for Rock and
OL,4,CRoll Hall of Fame induction
OL,6,F"We look forward to celebrating these
OL,7,Fremarkable artists at this year's
OL,8,Fceremony ` it's going to be an
OL,9,Funforgettable night."
OL,11,FAmong the honourees this year are Wu-
OL,12,FTang Clan, Queen Latifah, Luther
OL,13,FVandross and Latin superstar Celia
OL,14,FCruz.
OL,16,FBritish representation was more
OL,17,Flimited in 2025, with Bad Company and
OL,18,FJoe Cocker among the few UK acts
OL,19,Fhonoured.
