OL,3,COasis among Brits set for Rock and
OL,4,CRoll Hall of Fame induction
OL,6,FArtists are eligible for inclusion in
OL,7,Fthe hall 25 years after releasing
OL,8,Ftheir first commercial recording.
OL,10,FJoy Division, Oasis and Billy Idol
OL,11,Fwere among last year's nominees who
OL,12,Ffailed to make the cut.
OL,14,FThe 2026 Rock and Roll Hall of Fame
OL,15,Finduction ceremony will take place in
OL,16,FLos Angeles in November, before
OL,17,Fdebuting on Disney+ in December 2026.
OL,19,FMore than 1,200 artists, historians
OL,20,Fand music industry professionals vote
OL,21,Fto decide the nominees each year.
